    "To change which health data Health.md can access:\n\n1. Tap \"Open Health App\"\n2. Tap your profile icon (top right)\n3. Tap \"Apps\"\n4. Select \"Health.md\"\n5. Toggle permissions on or off": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So ändern Sie, auf welche Gesundheitsdaten Health.md zugreifen kann:\n\n1. Tippen Sie auf \"Health-App öffnen\"\n2. Tippen Sie auf Ihr Profilsymbol (oben rechts)\n3. Tippen Sie auf \"Apps\"\n4. Wählen Sie \"Health.md\"\n5. Schalten Sie Berechtigungen ein oder aus"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "To change which health data Health.md can access:\n\n1. Tap \"Open Health App\"\n2. Tap your profile icon (top right)\n3. Tap \"Apps\"\n4. Select \"Health.md\"\n5. Toggle permissions on or off"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para cambiar a qué datos de salud puede acceder Health.md:\n\n1. Toca \"Abrir aplicación de Salud\"\n2. Toca tu ícono de perfil (arriba a la derecha)\n3. Toca \"Apps\"\n4. Selecciona \"Health.md\"\n5. Activa o desactiva los permisos"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour modifier les données de santé auxquelles Health.md peut accéder :\n\n1. Touchez « Ouvrir l'app Santé »\n2. Touchez votre icône de profil (en haut à droite)\n3. Touchez « Apps »\n4. Sélectionnez « Health.md »\n5. Activez ou désactivez les autorisations"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Per modificare i dati sanitari a cui Health.md può accedere:\n\n1. Tocca \"Apri l'app Salute\"\n2. Tocca l'icona del profilo (in alto a destra)\n3. Tocca \"App\"\n4. Seleziona \"Health.md\"\n5. Attiva o disattiva i permessi"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Health.mdがアクセスできるヘルスデータを変更するには：\n\n1. \"ヘルスケアAppを開く\"をタップ\n2. プロフィールアイコン（右上）をタップ\n3. \"App\"をタップ\n4. \"Health.md\"を選択\n5. 権限のオン/オフを切り替え"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Health.md가 접근할 수 있는 건강 데이터를 변경하려면:\n\n1. \"건강 앱 열기\"를 탭하세요\n2. 프로필 아이콘(오른쪽 상단)을 탭하세요\n3. \"앱\"을 탭하세요\n4. \"Health.md\"를 선택하세요\n5. 권한을 켜거나 끄세요"
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Om te wijzigen welke gezondheidsgegevens Health.md kan openen:\n\n1. Tik op \"Gezondheid-app openen\"\n2. Tik op je profielpictogram (rechtsboven)\n3. Tik op \"Apps\"\n4. Selecteer \"Health.md\"\n5. Schakel machtigingen in of uit"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para alterar quais dados de saúde o Health.md pode acessar:\n\n1. Toque em \"Abrir App Saúde\"\n2. Toque no ícone do seu perfil (canto superior direito)\n3. Toque em \"Apps\"\n4. Selecione \"Health.md\"\n5. Ative ou desative as permissões"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "如需更改 Health.md 可以访问的健康数据：\n\n1. 点击「打开健康应用」\n2. 点击右上角的个人头像\n3. 点击「App」\n4. 选择「Health.md」\n5. 开启或关闭相应权限"
          }
        }
      }
    },
